<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/942334-i-am-an-avid-reader-and-have-read-more">I am an avid reader and have read more than 800 books. I fail to understand how this book is voted as a bestseller. How can anyone like the dimwit heroine Dougless(Duh gless is more like it)? The men in her life just walk all over her and the lady just doesn&#39;t get it. The beginning pages of book describing her relation with her boyfriend Robert was so pathetic that I just skimmed over the pages.</a>
</div>
