<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/14040194-sharon-behringer"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1351464436i/14040194._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
